data.message:
All my post aren't appearing in my friendlist newsfeed for 12 days already. I know this, because I asked a few friends when some 3 or 4 posts of mine got no interaction in succession and all of them said they never saw my posts. What is up and can I expect a response on this issue? 

Too many weird things happening on Facebook of late. There's another issue I'm massively upset about, but I've messaged and send so many reports to the support team about that (yet to hear anything back as usual though).

replies.message: Hi Sofia. Due to the volume of reports we receive, we're unable to reply to every one. We do review them all and appreciate your patience! -Anna
My post still aren't appearing in news feed.Reports have been send almost everyday.Please someone help me fix this!
